				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\texttt {Cond}^2\texttt {GANs}$$\end{document} benefits from low complexity and stable convergence which has been shown to be lacking in the previous approach.

